x": [195.8, 822.7, 1042.0, 839.3]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2014, we had $136 million of gross unrealized losses related to 67 fixed-rate CMOs that we", "bbox": [162.5, 869.5, 1076.9, 890.3]}, {"text": "invested in as part of our overall A/LM strategy. These securities had a weighted-average maturity of 4.6 years at", "bbox": [162.5, 894.5, 1108.5, 915.3]}, {"text": "December 31, 2014. Since these securities have a fixed interest rate, their fair value is sensitive to movements in", "bbox": [162.5, 919.5, 1101.2, 940.3]}, {"text": "market interest rates. We also had $1 million of gross unrealized losses related to 14 other mortgage-backed", "bbox": [162.5, 944.5, 1063.9, 965.3]}, {"text": "securities positions, which had a weighted-average maturity of 4.6 years at December 31, 2014. These unrealized", "bbox": [162.5, 969.5, 1107.5, 990.3]}, {"text": "losses are considered temporary since we expect to collect all contractually due amounts from these securities.", "bbox": [162.5, 994.5, 1084.2, 1015.3]}, {"text": "Accordingly, these investments were reduced to their fair value through OCI, not earnings.", "bbox": [162.5, 1019.5, 921.0, 1040.3]}, {"text": "We regularly assess our securities portfolio for OTTI. The assessments are based on the nature of the securities,", "bbox": [162.5, 1069.5, 1095.0, 1090.3]}, {"text": "the underlying collateral, the financial condition of the issuer, the extent and duration of the loss, our intent", "bbox": [162.5, 1094.5, 1056.5, 1115.3]}, {"text": "related to the individual securities, and the likelihood that we will have to sell securities prior to expected", "bbox": [162.5, 1119.5, 1041.5, 1140.3]}, {"text": "recovery.", "bbox": [162.5, 1144.5, 240.6, 1165.3]}, {"text": "161", "bbox": [621.9, 1484.1, 653.1, 1504.9]}]}